      • Serialized Fields

        • category

          String category
          Major area of the problem.

        • httpCode

          int httpCode
          If MetaClientException.category is MetaClientException.CATEGORY_HTTP, an HTTP response code. The server often uses these to inform the client in useful ways.

        • reason

          String reason

        • url

          String url
          A related baseUrl for certain errors such as upgrade scenarios.

        • request

          String request
          If the exception is the result of interaction with MDS, the request that was in progress. Otherwise, null.

        • response

          String response
          If the exception is the result of interaction with MDS, the response text (hopefully JSON) received. Otherwise, null.

        • message

          String message
